title: Did One of Health Canada’s Directors Responsible For Vaccine Rollout Just Commit Suicide???
cleaned_text:
According to his obituary: “Adam spent many years working at various levels of government, eventually holding the position of Director of Parliamentary Affairs at Health Canada. During the challenging times of the pandemic, Adam was part of the leadership team that led Canada’s health response to COVID-19.”

Meanwhile in New Zealand Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern Demands Citizens Report ‘Conspiracy Theorists’ Who ‘Oppose Gov’t Policies’ as ‘Terrorists’
